trans-unit.source: Contains methods and fields for UI Automation client applications.
trans-unit.target: Innehåller metoder och fält för en UI Automation-klientprogram.

trans-unit.source: Registers a method that handles [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] events.
trans-unit.target: Registrerar en metod som hanterar [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] händelser.

trans-unit.source: Some classes, such as <xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern>, expose fields identifying events that are specific to the class.
trans-unit.target: Vissa klasser, till exempel <xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern>, exponera fält som anger händelser som är specifika för klassen.</xref:System.Windows.Automation.GridPattern>

trans-unit.source: The AddAutomationEventHandler method provides a mechanism that enables you to register handlers for these events.
trans-unit.target: Metoden AddAutomationEventHandler tillhandahåller en mekanism som gör att du kan registrera hanterare för dessa händelser.

trans-unit.source: `eventHandler` can be an instance of the method, or a reference to the method (`AddressOf` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: `eventHandler`kan vara en instans av metoden, eller en referens till-metoden (`AddressOf` i Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: The identifier for the event the method will handle.
trans-unit.target: Identifierare för händelsen metoden hanterar.

trans-unit.source: The [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element to associate with the event handler.
trans-unit.target: Den [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element ska associeras med händelsehanteraren.

trans-unit.source: The scope of events to be handled; that is, whether they are on the element itself, or on its ancestors and descendants.
trans-unit.target: Vilka händelser som ska hanteras; det vill säga om de är på elementet i sig själv eller dess överordnade och underordnade.

trans-unit.source: The method to call when the specified event occurs.
trans-unit.target: Metoden som ska anropas när den angivna händelsen inträffar.

trans-unit.source: Registers a method that will handle focus-changed events.
trans-unit.target: Registrerar en metod som hanterar fokus ändras händelser.

trans-unit.source: Focus-changed events are system-wide; you cannot set a narrower scope.
trans-unit.target: Fokus ändras händelser är systemomfattande; Du kan inte ange mindre omfattning.

trans-unit.source: `eventHandler` can be an instance of the method, or a reference to the method (`AddressOf` in Visual Basic).
trans-unit.target: `eventHandler`kan vara en instans av metoden, eller en referens till-metoden (`AddressOf` i Visual Basic).

trans-unit.source: The method to call when the event occurs.
trans-unit.target: Metoden som ska anropas när händelsen inträffar.

trans-unit.source: Compares two integer arrays containing run-time [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] to determine whether their content is the same.
trans-unit.target: Jämför två heltal matriser som innehåller körning [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] att avgöra om innehållet är samma.

trans-unit.source: If either of the arguments is a null reference (`Nothing` in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_visualbnet](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-visualbnet-md.md)]), Compare throws an <xref:System.ArgumentNullException> exception.
trans-unit.target: Om något av argumenten är en null-referens (`Nothing` i [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_visualbnet](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-visualbnet-md.md)]), jämför returnerar ett <xref:System.ArgumentNullException>undantag.</xref:System.ArgumentNullException>

trans-unit.source: The first run-time [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-id-md.md)] to compare.
trans-unit.target: Den första körning [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-id-md.md)] ska jämföras.

trans-unit.source: The second run-time [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-id-md.md)] to compare.
trans-unit.target: Den andra körning [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-id-md.md)] ska jämföras.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the compared run-time [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] refer to the same [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] element; otherwise <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om jämfört med körning [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_id#plural](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-idsharpplural-md.md)] referera till samma [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_ui](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-ui-md.md)] element, annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Compares two [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] elements, returning <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if both refer to the same [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] element.
trans-unit.target: Jämför två [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element, returnerar <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""> </xref> om båda refererar till samma [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_ui](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] element.

trans-unit.source: If either of the arguments is a null reference (`Nothing` in [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_visualbnet](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-visualbnet-md.md)]), <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Automation.Compare%2A> throws an <xref:System.ArgumentNullException> exception.
trans-unit.target: Om något av argumenten är en null-referens (`Nothing` i [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_visualbnet](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-visualbnet-md.md)]), <xref:System.Windows.Automation.Automation.Compare%2A>utlöser ett <xref:System.ArgumentNullException>undantag.</xref:System.ArgumentNullException> </xref:System.Windows.Automation.Automation.Compare%2A>

trans-unit.target: Andra [!INCLUDE[TLA2#tla_uiautomation](~/add/includes/tla2sharptla-uiautomation-md.md)] element ska jämföras.
